    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_1052-1116",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1052-1116",
      "markText": "徐天啸痛惜地认为：“中国之女子，既无高尚之旨趣，又无奇特之思想；既无独立之主义，又无伟大之事业。廉耻尽丧，依赖性成，奈何奈何。”",
      "totalCount": 520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1052&rangeEnd=1116",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1052&rangeEnd=1116"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_18_1417-1451",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1417-1451",
      "markText": "现世社会的价值考量，往往只在乎产量或结果，忽视了事情变化的过程本身。",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1417&rangeEnd=1451",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1417&rangeEnd=1451"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_4434-4534",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "4434-4534",
      "markText": "我以为，受害的“封建”女性形象之所以根深蒂固，在某种程度上是出自一种分析上的混淆，即错误地将标准的规定视为经历过的现实，这种混淆的出现，是因缺乏某种历史性的考察，即从女性自身的视角来考察其所处的世界。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4434&rangeEnd=4534",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4434&rangeEnd=4534"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_22_5283-5311",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "5283-5311",
      "markText": "也证明了由阅读这一看似随意的行动所带来的耗费精力的危险。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=5283&rangeEnd=5311",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=5283&rangeEnd=5311"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_8238-8306",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "8238-8306",
      "markText": "儒家社会性别体系之所以能长期延续，应归之于相当大范围内的灵活性，在这一范围内，各种阶层、地区和年龄的女性，都在实践层面享受着生活的乐趣。",
      "totalCount": 276,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8238&rangeEnd=8306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8238&rangeEnd=8306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_18_1582-1615",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1582-1615",
      "markText": "困在斗室过着小日子时才认识到，真正的自由，是与活动空间大小无关的。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1582&rangeEnd=1615",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1582&rangeEnd=1615"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_19_783-880",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "783-880",
      "markText": "古代史的杜芳琴、秦汉史的李贞德，唐宋史的邓小南、臧健、高世瑜、刘静贞，明清史的定宜庄、李伯重、熊秉真、刘咏聪。明清妇女文学研究，对妇女史尤多启发，我特别感谢张宏生和他的女弟子，还有华玮、胡晓真。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=783&rangeEnd=880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=783&rangeEnd=880"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_24_10173-10215",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "10173-10215",
      "markText": "虽然缠足对男性有着性欲吸引力，但如果没有相关女性的合作，缠足是不可能长存千年之久的。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10173&rangeEnd=10215",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10173&rangeEnd=10215"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_1673-1755",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1673-1755",
      "markText": "总之，受父权压迫的女性，成了旧中国落后的一个缩影，成了当时遭受屈辱的根源。受压迫的封建女性形象，被赋予了如此强烈的民族主义情绪，以至最终变成一种无可置疑的历史真理。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1673&rangeEnd=1755",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1673&rangeEnd=1755"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_8876-8952",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "8876-8952",
      "markText": "各阶层的妇女中间并无共同利益。因此，即使是明末清初最具文化资源的妇女，也无从在概念上锻造起一个有广泛社会基础的统一战线，从制度上向社会性别体系发起进攻。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8876&rangeEnd=8952",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8876&rangeEnd=8952"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_9933-9979",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "9933-9979",
      "markText": "儒家的社会性别体系为何在如此长的时间内运转得这样灵活顺畅？妇女们从这一体系中获得过什么好处？",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9933&rangeEnd=9979",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9933&rangeEnd=9979"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_23598-23632",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "23598-23632",
      "markText": "她们不是儒家文化权力运作的受害者，而是有份操纵这一权力的既得利益者。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=23598&rangeEnd=23632",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=23598&rangeEnd=23632"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_8384-8435",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "8384-8435",
      "markText": "我的论点是，“三从”这一规范，无疑剥夺了女性的法律人格和独立的社会身份，但她的个性或主观性并未被剥夺。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8384&rangeEnd=8435",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8384&rangeEnd=8435"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_1302-1411",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1302-1411",
      "markText": "当帝国主义侵略加剧时，受害女性成了中华民族本身的象征——被男性外国强权“强奸”和征服。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1411",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1411"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_18_1817-1842",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1817-1842",
      "markText": "我恭敬诚恳地把我的处女作，献给过去和未来的读者们。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1817&rangeEnd=1842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1817&rangeEnd=1842"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_24_39888-39980",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "39888-39980",
      "markText": "这些妇女尽其所能，在赋予她们的空间内，创造着意义和尊严。没有认识到她们的自豪和满足，就去哀痛她们的无知或去谴责压迫她们的体系，这是对明末清初中国妇女生活和社会性别体系最本质面貌的忽视。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056405&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=39888&rangeEnd=39980",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8dd32550813ab7c88g0154f6?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=39888&rangeEnd=39980"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056405_20_6887-7023",
